
* to view only one selected forecast information

http://localhost/cic_latest/index.php/weather/view_forecast/2013-09-17
															___________ is selected date for which we want to have 
																		forecast information.


* to view all records in one page

http://localhost/cic_latest/index.php/weather/view_forecast/


* to view all pages (with pagination)

http://localhost/cic_latest/index.php/weather/view_forecast/pages/